        <h2>About</h2>	
  	<h1>I am a PhD student at Laboratoire de Physique Subatomique et de Cosmologie (LPSC) in  Grenoble, France. My supervisor is Pr. Aurélien Barrau, a group member of both LSST and AMS experiments, and Head of the Master in Subatomique and Astroparticle Physics at Grenoble University, which I graduated from in June 2014. <br/><br/>
	  I am also a fellow of &Eacute;cole Normale Supérieure de Lyon since 2009. This prestigeous instutions has been providing me with a genereous scolarship for the whole duration of my undergraduate studies, as well as the grant for my PhD studies. 
